data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located in the prestigious Sterling Lakes, section 3 gated community on the lake. This charming residence offers a spacious open-concept design that welcomes you with comfortable natural lighting, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. Situated on the lake, this property offers not only a tranquil waterfront setting but also unobstructed views of the beautiful surroundings with no neighbors sharing the green space to the left of the home. The kitchen features granite countertops and an ample amount of workspace, including a conveniently high breakfast bar. The primary en-suite bathroom is located on the first floor and offers a retreat featuring a large soaking tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day, all while enjoying picturesque views of the lake. Upstairs is an additional 4 bedrooms and a second living space. Outback you have an over sized yard with opportunity for your own private oasis.
